     C**************************************************************************
      ** PRESS S/R TO MOVE THE APPROPRIATE VALUES INTO FIELD WWAID,
      ** DEPENDING ON WHICH FUNCTION KEY HAS BEEN PRESSED.
     C**************************************************************************
